<lg n="stanza_title">
<lg>
<l>To Eteri Svanidze</l>
</lg>
<lg>
<l>In ancient times, here, they used to help the army,</l>
<l>With a drum and bugle,</l>
<l>Now, a poppy greets me</l>
<l>Like the light of a beautiful woman.</l>
<l>It comes to greet me, it illuminates me,</l>
<l>It throws sparkles towards me</l>
<l>The blossoming of the alucha and wild plum,</l>
<l>And brought good news of the spring...</l>
<l>When she recognized me as a stranger,</l>
<l>She grew timid and lowered her head;</l>
<l>She grew timid and lowered her head,</l>
<l>A blush rose up through her,</l>
<l>Maybe, she was thinking of this,</l>
<l>Does he like me, or not?!</l>
</lg>
<lg>
<l>1940</l>
</lg>
</lg>
